OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,Fhead coach Arne Slot has given his
OL,7,Fbacking to Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,8,Fafter the departing defender was booed
OL,9,Fby large sections of the Anfield crowd
OL,10,Fduring the 2-2 Premier League draw
OL,11,Fwith Arsenal.
OL,13,FAlexander-Arnold was brought on as a
OL,14,F67th-minute substitute against the
OL,15,FGunners and, along with some of his
OL,16,Fteam-mates, seemed bemused by his
OL,17,Fhostile reception.
