OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,FThe right-back is expected to join
OL,7,FSpanish giants Real Madrid, after
OL,8,Fannouncing he was not signing a new
OL,9,Fdeal at Anfield.
OL,11,FSlot said: "The thing I consider is I
OL,12,Fwant to win a game of football and if
OL,13,Fwe think we can win with Trent, I owe
OL,14,Fit to his team-mates and to the fans,
OL,15,Fbecause they (Liverpool) hired me to
OL,16,Fwin as many games of football as
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,19,F"And if I think there's a better
OL,20,Fchance of winning with Trent, then I
OL,21,Fwill (pick him).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
