OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,F"If I think it's a distraction or
OL,7,Fwhatever can happen for us not to play
OL,8,Fa good game of football, then I might
OL,9,Fmake another decision.
OL,11,F"But I think Trent showed today why I
OL,12,Fbrought him in because he was very
OL,13,Fclose with a few fantastic crosses for
OL,14,Fus to win the game."
OL,16,FAlexander-Arnold looked upset at the
OL,17,Ffinal whistle as team-mate Luis Diaz
OL,18,Fand even the Arsenal manager Mikel
OL,19,FArteta giving him a hug.
