OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,F"It is definitely difficult for him,"
OL,7,Fsaid Slot.
OL,9,F"Maybe he is positively surprised how
OL,10,Fthe reactions were. It was clear there
OL,11,Fwere mixed reactions - it wasn't all
OL,12,Fnegative.
OL,14,F"I am not sure if he has negative
OL,15,Ffeelings about today...maybe, maybe, I
OL,16,Fhaven't spoken to him."
