OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool defender Jamie
OL,7,FCarragher told Sky Sports: "Booing one
OL,8,Fof your own players while they are
OL,9,Fplaying is not for me. That was a step
OL,10,Ftoo far.
OL,12,F"That could've been his last
OL,13,Fperformance, which might be the right
OL,14,Fthing as Liverpool don't need a
OL,15,Fcircus."
OL,17,FSlot had said before the match he
OL,18,Fwould not tell how fans to react and
OL,19,Fhe maintained that stance afterwards.
