OL,3,CLiverpool manager Slot backs Trent
OL,4,Cafter barrage of Anfield boos
OL,6,F"It's a privilege to live in Europe
OL,7,Fwhere everyone can have his own
OL,8,Fopinion and express their own opinion
OL,9,Fand that is what we saw today," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,F"All of them are not happy with him
OL,13,Fleaving the club but a few of them
OL,14,Fshowed it in a way that they booed him
OL,15,Fand some of them clapped."
OL,17,FAlexander-Arnold's long-time team-mate
OL,18,FAndy Robertson told Sky Sports: "It's
OL,19,Fnot nice to see a friend get booed, it
OL,20,Fwasn't nice. But as I said, we can't
OL,21,Ftell people how to act.
